officers. I couldn't read a note. I just had to go by

14:02.008 --> 14:07.254
ear, you know, to find out what came next, so to 
speak. And that was really my first introduction

14:08.175 --> 14:10.797
to the big band.

14:14.581 --> 14:18.465
And that National Guard thing only lasted two 
weeks. I didn't join the National Guard. I was

14:20.513 --> 14:27.405
going as a substitute for a man, a member of the band 
in the National Guard who could not go. So they put

14:28.146 --> 14:31.772
me into his team and so forth. Did y'all, was your 
primary task to play for National Guard dances?

14:37.402 --> 14:38.464
