music? No, we weren't. Dance music? Yeah. Of

14:43.454 --> 14:55.185
course, they had a band, you know, and these 
people, the rest of the people were members of the

14:43.454 --> 14:55.185
band, and this was kind of an offshoot of the band, 
you know, various ones. Of course, they didn't

14:55.205 --> 15:01.171
have a piano band, and they substituted me in 
there. I don't know how it was expanded, but

15:01.191 --> 15:07.276
anyway, I learned a lot from going back. I went to 
three different years of camp in the National

15:07.296 --> 15:12.381
Guard. ever worry about a young Baptist boy 
playing dance music? I've never heard of it.

15:19.905 --> 15:22.209
