know, Fred, I don't think you ought to come to New 
York. I said, why not? Well, I didn't ask him that

19:30.931 --> 19:35.057
right now, but I said, no, I've always wanted to go 
to Indiana, and I'm going to stay. He said, if you

19:35.077 --> 19:35.918
want to. So later on, he did tell me, he said, well, 
you were dressed like you, you know, you'd given up

19:36.505 --> 19:48.583
a good job, but probably hadn't the best clothes 
